HB 286 Original 2026 Regular Session Berault
Abstract: Repeals certain authority relative to the St. Tammany Mosquito Abatement
District.
Present law provides that the board of commissioners of the St. Tammany Mosquito
Abatement District exercises sole authority for determining the manner in which funds of
the district are expended for purposes of mosquito abatement, control, eradication, and study
subject to the approval of the director of the district.
